DRAGONBORN
Ability Score Increase: STR +2, CHA +1
Size: Medium
Speed: 30ft

BREATH TYPE AND WIDTH
Black: Acid, 5 by 30 ft. line (Dex save)
Blue: Lightening, 5 by 30 ft. line (Dex save)
Brass: Fire, 5 by 30 ft. line (Dex save)
Bronze: Lightening, 5 by 30 ft. line (Dex save)
Copper: Acid, 5 by 30 ft. line (Dex save)
Gold: Fire, 15 ft. cone (Dex save)
Green: Poison, 15 ft. cone (Dex save)
Red: Fire, 15 ft. cone (Dex save)
Silver: Cold, 15 ft. cone (Con save)
White: Cold, 15 ft. cone (Con save)

Draconic Ancestry: Choose a dragon type (color). Breath weapon and damage resistance are determined by color.
Breath Weapon: DC for saving throw is 8 + Con + Proficiency (Creature takes 2d6 on failed, hald on save)
                Damages increases 3d6 at 6th level, 4d6 at 11th level, 5d6 at 16th level.
Languages: Common and Draconic
       
